public final class MapsEngineLayerInfo

A class to encapsulate information identifying the Maps Engine layer. A layer can be identified in two different ways:

  • As part of a map to which the layer belongs via the the map's asset ID and the layer's key within the map.
  • Directly via the layer's asset ID.
If both are specified, we will use the information from the first method as canonical.
